The '''TzHaar-Mej''' are both the leaders of the [[TzHaar]] people and powerful mages. They fight with both melee and magic using their [[Toktz-mej-tal|staves]]. When attacked within 6 squares of other higher level TzHaar ([[TzHaar-Ket|Ket]] and [[TzHaar-Xil|Xil]]), the mage will cry out "Kot kl, zek e JalYt!" which roughly translates to "Save me, attack the human!" This will cause the nearby TzHaar to aid the TzHaar-Mej in combat.

